{"tid":1917960,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"美麗新香港","createTime":"2020-03-09T20:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T12:43:55.000Z","uid":431,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7591d47859302871599a9e7f854bebdb7b529910","tid":1917960,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T20:23:20.000Z","msg":"自你決定要走以後 <br />\n沒人知我有多難受 <br />\n再沒勇氣在派對逗留 <br />\n踫見朋友不敢問候  <br />\n自你遠去不再回頭 <br />\n青山綠水不再依舊 <br />\n再沒有早起身的理由 <br />\n再沒可安睡的枕頭  <br />\n這世界只有一種鄉愁 <br />\n就是沒有你的時候 <br />\n這香港已不是我的地頭 <br />\n就當我在外地旅遊  <br />\n<br />\n自美夢再不可尋求 <br />\n我便學會清風兩袖 <br />\n命運要令我學識奮鬥 <br />\n但我只懂得荒謬  <br />\n這世界只有一種鄉愁 <br />\n是你不在身邊的時候 <br />\n這香港已不是我的地頭 <br />\n就當我在外地飄流  <br />\n<br />\n我知已走到盡頭 <br />\n為何還要擔憂 <br />\n這世界也不是我的地頭 <br />\n就當我在宇宙飄流<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb639f0f38fc5611bc300ee43fa0cb20187206a8","tid":1917960,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T20:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff74b27b9fd5c29d25a5e1f7a2c3c6b88d463e2","tid":1917960,"uid":309002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T21:59:32.000Z","msg":"第一次聽好似係睇金像獎<br />\n<br />\n最記得 就當我在外地旅遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12c2234d0471d5264a07084b72b5ac13c197fba","tid":1917960,"uid":313514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T22:25:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7e68a377373ec070accd04539fb3d5b1e933535","tid":1917960,"uid":122110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T12:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}